          "body": "<h2>Beatles Tribute Night at Vesica Santuario on July 26</h2>\n<p>Concert Nights brings a Beatles Tribute Edition to Vesica Santuario on July 26, 2026. This is a close, acoustic concert built around voice, strings, and guest players, with Manuel Negrete on cello, Mayte Caamal and Eduardo Vásquez on violin, and Josías Sánchez on viola. If you want a music-led night instead of a standard club format, this is the clear reason to book.</p>\n<h3>Live Strings, Candlelight, and a Familiar Songbook</h3>\n<p>The bill centers on Beatles songs played in a stripped-back format, with live instrumentation doing the work rather than a DJ set. The setup is intimate and candlelit, which fits the room and puts the focus on the arrangements, the players, and the songs themselves. For anyone looking through Vesica Santuario events in Tulum this July, this one stands out for its chamber-style lineup and a set built on songs most people already know.</p>\n<p>The venue also pairs the concert with food and drinks, so the night is built to last longer than the set alone. That makes it a solid pick if you want a seated show with real musicians up front, not background music.</p>\n<h3>Plan Ahead for a Small-Room Concert</h3>\n<p>No door time, set time, or ticket tiers are confirmed here, so the smart move is to book before the night fills up. The format is intimate, and the room is set for a close listening crowd rather than a walk-in party. Secure your seats on this page for the July 26 concert at Vesica Santuario.</p>",
